  "body": "zksync.js uses ethers 5.0 as a [peer dependency](https://github.com/matter-labs/zksync/blob/2990cfa294d50b87f8d3ccb3c3f418cc2d0d5a40/js/zksync.js/package.json#L14) however if the application has ethers 4.0 then it can't find `BigNumber` because in ethers 4.0 it's under `ethers.utils.BigNumber` rather than `ethers.BigNumber`:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2020-08-28 10-45-01](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/168240/91599841-c4996f00-e91b-11ea-9f9d-b9f29132e6f0.png)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2020-08-28 10-44-52](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/168240/91599853-c82cf600-e91b-11ea-8238-963b28d72e39.png)\r\n\r\nA suggestion is to publish a new zksync version which has ethers 5.0 bundled in under a release tag.\r\n\r\nAnother suggestion is to support both versions in code but that seems like a bigger task. ",
