    "body": "Turns out it's possible to use npm aliases to use multiple versions of the same package:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i ethers@4 \r\nnpm i ethers5@npm:ethers@5 \r\n```\r\n\r\nSolved my problem so closing issue.",
